Eating disorders â€“ descriptive stats

Caricamento del pacchetto richiesto: viridisLite
thedat <- readRDS(
  here::here(
    "data", "processed", "quest", "demo_info_quest.rds"
  )
)
thedat$diagnosis <- factor(thedat$diagnosis, levels = c("AN", "BN", "RI", "HC"))
d <- thedat %>% 
  dplyr::select(
    age, sex, diagnosis,
    ws, rws, bmi,
    bsq14_tot, ros_tot, dass21_stress, dass21_anxiety, dass21_dep, sias_tot,
    mps_cmd, mps_ps, mps_pepc, mps_or, orto_tot, dieting, bulimia, oral_control,
  ) %>% 
  dplyr::filter(sex == "Femmina")
d %>%
  group_by(diagnosis) %>% 
  summarise(across(where(is.numeric), ~ round(mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE), 2)))
d %>%
  group_by(diagnosis) %>% 
  summarise(across(where(is.numeric), ~ round(mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE), 2)))

d %>%
  group_by(diagnosis) %>% 
  summarise(across(where(is.numeric), ~ sd(.x, na.rm = TRUE) / sqrt(n())))
d %>% ggplot(aes(x=diagnosis, y=bmi, fill=diagnosis)) +
  geom_violin(width=1.4) +
  geom_boxplot(width=0.1, color="grey", alpha=0.2) +
  scale_fill_viridis(discrete = TRUE) +
  theme(
    legend.position="none",
    plot.title = element_text(size=11)
  ) +
  ggtitle("BMI") +
  ylab("") +
  xlab("Diagnosis")

d %>% ggplot(aes(x=diagnosis, y=ros_tot, fill=diagnosis)) +
